NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::CheckChangesTests - release tests for checking
    changes

VERSION
    version 1.100700

SYNOPSIS
    In "dist.ini":

        [CheckChangesTests]

DESCRIPTION
    This is an extension of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::InlineFiles, providing the
    following files

      xt/release/check-changes.t - a standard Test::CheckChanges test

INSTALLATION
    See perlmodinstall for information and options on installing Perl
    modules.

AUTHOR
      Marcel Gruenauer <marcel@cpan.org>

